{"tid":521093,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"身為毒撚，一定要學識手語","createTime":"2018-01-06T06:56:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-03T15:24:42.000Z","uid":24165,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3a90a4452541f67f48f09e8118f5142da65ff8d6","tid":521093,"uid":24165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T06:56:58.000Z","msg":"學識手語可以唔洗開口同人講野 <br />\n唔洗「呃⋯」好耐 <br />\n唔洗擔心會dead air<br />\n講秘密唔會比人偷聽 <br />\n唔洗驚比人話冇禮貌<br />\n搭小巴唔敢嗌有落都唔會有人笑你<br />\n因為手語簡單直接<br />\n所有野用身體動作<br />\n早幾日返工見到個聽障人士<br />\n我一做個手勢佢就知我明白佢 <br />\n係嘈雜既環境 我地用手語傾計<br />\n透過眼神流露情感 其他人只能默默咁望住我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n世界仿佛好似得返我同佢 <br />\n一切回到原始年代 突破語言既界限<br />\n以最純粹既心靈交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望可以多啲人學 <br />\n即使唔常用 但係某啲情況總會用得著 <br />\n好想以後都用手語溝通 唔想再打開口<br />\n好想瘋狂用手語呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"024b6db2c4afcf837bdd5d00f7acb7ad7a9bc42a","tid":521093,"uid":24165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T07:15:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a03d486b1666ca62e62468eb523e6b71bc1a3aa","tid":521093,"uid":24165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T11:27:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9e9a31a865794eae8afc669e058acdde3079c94","tid":521093,"uid":24165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T11:56:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"442b95e0adf55c345b68edfaf91ce603cabecb81","tid":521093,"uid":24165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T13:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  推到1001"},{"pid":"1712acd06afea22afc50cf67202e40e49e20fa4c","tid":521093,"uid":161998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T13:54:02.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"2753de4a166b79739ed08ff64b42756bceffa6cd","tid":521093,"uid":116364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T18:51:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3a406f7b2ae541b9b0e96a50ad67ecfa8ddfd84e","tid":521093,"uid":113546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T19:26:28.000Z","msg":"最近毒到同樓主有一樣既諗法<br />\n越黎越黎唔想講野 好驚同人有言語交流 <br />\n寧願用手語都唔想講野 咁好似舒服好多 <br />\n而且仲可以聽住歌咁同人溝通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2671d946d67b4574ee731d94ea476722a1c0d9e4","tid":521093,"uid":71883,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T19:47:51.000Z","msg":"手語靠既唔單止係隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n表情同身體語言都好重要<br />\n<br />\n當一個毒撚連野都唔想講既時候<br />\n<br />\n你覺得仲會唔會做到表情同身體語言都豐富到令人地明佢想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\n屌，係咪認真左"},{"pid":"37bc12c76c206dbbc742f51047a164611600bee5","tid":521093,"uid":161821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T19:49:04.000Z","msg":"之前諗過學 當多個技能"},{"pid":"a05a3ac7e0586c90017768819d1bf406dbd21915","tid":521093,"uid":93492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T15:24:42.000Z","msg":"絲打你方唔方便留個Tg?<br />\n有啲嘢想請教你"}]}